"Test #deq — símbolos avanzados
'<hr/>
"1. Integrales
#deq M(x) = $Integral{0; L}(q*x)*dx = q*L^2/2

'<hr/>
"2. Derivadas
#deq V(x) = dM/dx = q*x

'<hr/>
"3. Ecuación diferencial
#deq E*I*d^2*y/dx^2 = M(x) = -P*x

'<hr/>
"4. Matriz de rigidez con doble igualdad
#deq K_e = E*I/L^3*[12; 6*L; -12; 6*L | 6*L; 4*L^2; -6*L; 2*L^2 | -12; -6*L; 12; -6*L | 6*L; 2*L^2; -6*L; 4*L^2]

'<hr/>
"5. Ecuación matricial completa
#deq [F_1; M_1; F_2; M_2] = E*I/L^3*[12; 6*L; -12; 6*L | 6*L; 4*L^2; -6*L; 2*L^2 | -12; -6*L; 12; -6*L | 6*L; 2*L^2; -6*L; 4*L^2]*[v_1; θ_1; v_2; θ_2]

'<hr/>
"6. Triple igualdad con fracciones
#deq ω_n = sqr(k/m) = sqr(E*I/(ρ*A*L^4)) = 2*π*f_n
